{"tid":1115214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發現無戴眼鏡出街成個人即刻懵哂","createTime":"2019-04-19T04:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T05:50:03.000Z","uid":61832,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da7a5a5f02bb9e665f89f19f34a81467452c2149","tid":1115214,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:37:54.000Z","msg":"本身同老婆同個歲半仔開開心心返支那去長隆<br />\n<br />\n出門口搵唔到眼鏡心諗200幾度睇遠野唔清就算啦<br />\n<br />\n坐69x去到大欖落車後發現成個銀包跌係巴士度<br />\n<br />\n即刻打去站頭睇下會唔會有同即刻坐車去站頭睇<br />\n<br />\n最後當然係無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位連登仔歡迎盡情恥笑小弟抵撚死好人好姐返支那抵撚死<br />\n但恥笑同時如果你咁啱同小弟坐同一班車執到麻煩留個言等我搵你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n19/4/2019<br />\n九巴69x <br />\n09:14係大欖隧道落車<br />\n<br />\n銀包係黑色。類似證件套 <br />\n入面有1張恆生卡 1張匯豐卡<br />\n身份證 回鄉證 員工證<br />\n小量現金<br />\n有我仔幅相同我同老婆合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全能連登賜我力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：已報失"},{"pid":"ddb78a73f27c67c80a14a5f5503d53ae0b2b7dfb","tid":1115214,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"自屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f424047a337026f637f069628ecf1467da4c61e8","tid":1115214,"uid":165373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4767f856d8b751f37166040fed5f6b3b47c4e5a5","tid":1115214,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db7f4fccafa6de262e775882f2535ab78f3c1b2","tid":1115214,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ce98115bb12f34e5ea89a8421749379327484c","tid":1115214,"uid":67455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:03:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"722b9e0a2cdc01e99b5ae2880a24ecc199918ab5","tid":1115214,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:27:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"57da48f55e00f2b39bb5a26e51ed42defad413ee","tid":1115214,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}